OL,6,FEquality and Human Rights Commission
OL,7,F(EHRC) chairwoman Baroness Kishwer
OL,8,FFalkner said the ruling provided
OL,9,Fclarity to organisations and they
OL,10,Fshould be "taking care" to look at the
OL,11,F"very readable judgment".
OL,13,F"Single-sex services like changing
OL,14,Frooms must be based on biological
OL,15,Fsex," she told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,16,FProgramme.
OL,18,F"If a male person is allowed to use a
OL,19,Fwomen-only service or facility, it
OL,20,Fisn't any longer single-sex, then it
OL,21,Fbecomes a mixed-sex space.
