OL,11,F"But I have to say, there's no law
OL,12,Fthat forces organisations, service
OL,13,Fproviders, to provide a single-sex
OL,14,Fspace, and there is no law against
OL,15,Fthem providing a third space, an
OL,16,Fadditional space, such as unisex
OL,17,Ftoilets for example, or changing
OL,18,Frooms."
