OL,6,FShe suggested trans rights
OL,7,Forganisations "should be using their
OL,8,Fpowers of advocacy to ask for those
OL,9,Fthird spaces".
OL,11,FThe decision by the Supreme Court was
OL,12,Fhailed by women's rights campaigners,
OL,13,Fbut trans communities are "devastated"
OL,14,Fby the ruling.
OL,16,FHelen Belcher, the chair of
OL,17,FTransActual, said: "The Supreme Court
OL,18,Fchose not to hear from any trans
OL,19,Fpeople, preferring instead to listen
OL,20,Fto exclusionary groups.
