OL,6,FShe added: "They have rights, and
OL,7,Ftheir rights must be respected ` then
OL,8,Fit becomes a victory for common sense."
OL,10,FShe added: "It's not a victory for an
OL,11,Fincrease in unpleasant actions against
OL,12,Ftrans people. We will not tolerate that
OL,14,F"We stand here to defend trans people
OL,15,Fas much as we do anyone else. So I
OL,16,Fwant to make that very clear."
